high_descs: Turn around and walk across the room to the dining table.
Pick up the blue bowl from the dining table.
Turn right and walk to the refrigerator.
Put the bowl in the refrigerator for a few seconds, then take it out and close the refrigerator.
Move slightly back away from the refrigerator.
Put the bowl in the bottom cabinet to the right of the refrigerator, then close the cabinet.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooled bowl inside a cabinet.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the table.
Grab the bowl on the table.
Carrying the bowl, walk to the fridge to your right.
Place the bowl inside the fridge to chill it, then remove the bowl.
Carrying the cold bowl, walk to the counter cabinet to your right.
Place the cold bowl inside the cabinet.
anns.task_desc: Place a cold bowl in the cabinet.

high_descs: Turn around and go to the table across the room.
Pick up the bowl on the table, in front of the pump bottle and spatula.
Turn to your right and go to the refrigerator.
Place the bowl in the refrigerator, wait a moment for the bowl to get chilled, then remove the bowl from the refrigerator.
Move back and to your right, so that you are in front of the small cabinet to the left of the stove.
Place the bowl in the lower cabinet, to the left of the stove.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled bowl in the cabinet.
